				<h2>A definition of the term</h2>	
<font size="5">
<ul>
<li class="fragment">2016: After 8 years of workshop</li>

				</ul>
<div class="fragment">
<blockquote >
Editorialization is the set of dynamics that produce and structure digital space. These dynamics can be understood as the interactions of individual and collective actions within a particular digital environment.
</blockquote>
<p align="right">Vitali-Rosati, <i>What is editorialization?</i>, Sens public 2016</p></div>
</font>
<p align="center" class="fragment">What does it mean???</p>


